title: Vytoč mého agenta
overview: Call My Agent tells comedic stories from a casting agency. Every day is full of work and human pitfalls. Trying to satisfy the demanding needs of acting stars, a constant battle with competition, complicated personal relationships that often get mixed up in work matters. The agency team has to manage all of this and survive the daily struggle that brings with it many absurd and comical situations, as well as touching moments and real human dramas.
